Class AbstractConsoleRunnerWithHistory<T extends LanguageConsoleView>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.execution.runners.AbstractConsoleRunnerWithHistory<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroovyShellRunnerImpl

    public abstract class AbstractConsoleRunnerWithHistory<T extends LanguageConsoleView>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides basic functionality for running consoles. It launches external process and handles line input with history
